    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来试试这款兽人与拉霸机完美结合的竞技游戏，带领兽人们为了胜利向敌方进军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/c3cdc0f2207953c035cdeb77329af2da.poster.avif?t=1769421872\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/c3cdc0f2207953c035cdeb77329af2da.webm?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/c3cdc0f2207953c035cdeb77329af2da.mp4?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >画风独特的兽人们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《兽人大作战》中，对战前需要从独特各种之中组成一套阵容。要注意，它们之间有自己的团体，当团体的“领袖”被选择时加成会被激活，这将极大的影响你游玩时的选择的策略风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/eb9609c4f2bc2462bc930844c33a0e5e.poster.avif?t=1769421872\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/eb9609c4f2bc2462bc930844c33a0e5e.webm?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/eb9609c4f2bc2462bc930844c33a0e5e.mp4?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>世界挑战，挥斥方遒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带上你的兽人勇者，与不同的NPC展开交战。通过巧妙的排兵布阵和策略对决，不断击败对手，解锁更多兽人伙伴，壮大你的阵容，打造属于你的强大兽人大军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/ca880f5af0b07c4e5e3b5c9b1171af7b.poster.avif?t=1769421872\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/ca880f5af0b07c4e5e3b5c9b1171af7b.webm?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/ca880f5af0b07c4e5e3b5c9b1171af7b.mp4?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略与运气并存的同屏竞技</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管拉下拉杆就能召唤兽人，但你仍需为胜利准备好对应的策略。在合适的时机选择双倍下注，控制金币节奏的同时获得更高收益。在转盘三连时获得的英雄也是扭转战局的利器，他们拥有不同的进场技能和buff效果。观察战局，冷静地使用它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/945d3a88f780957e7b89719af78cf32b.poster.avif?t=1769421872\" width=1068 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/945d3a88f780957e7b89719af78cf32b.webm?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158040/extras/945d3a88f780957e7b89719af78cf32b.mp4?t=1769421872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
